        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>Don't wanna be that man </l>
          <l>don't wanna feel like a stain upon your shame </l>
          <l>don't wanna go when it's turning late </l>
          <l>just wanna be with you </l>
          <l>and drink lemonade </l>
          <l>oh can't you see </l>
