          <l>don't wanna walk alone in the rain </l>
          <l>just wanna be with you </l>
          <l>and chill in the back </l>
          <l>oh can't you see </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>Cause when i'm waching you </l>
          <l>you look a little sad </l>
          <l>Come on baby be with me </l>
          <l>i'm gonna make it o.k </l>
          <l>Gonna make you smile </l>
          <l>Gonna make you feel free </l>
          <l>Give me your heart </l>
          <l>Baby you will see</l>
